<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Israel-Crumbling Fronts, 2nd Ld,0820 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Troubles on two fronts as Israel gears for elections
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; Eds: CORRECTS first reference to Shahak, graf 28. Picks up 29th
graf pvs &QL; 
 &UR; AP Photos &QL; 
