 &UR; YACHTING:
	   SYDNEY, Australia _ Brindabella skipper George Snow predicts a
close struggle among the three leading contenders for line honors
in the annual Sydney-to-Hobart yacht race. The fleet of 115 has
been warned to prepare for the possibility of showers and
thunderstorms after the race begins Saturday.
